--- AI & Slop Note (informational; the license above already covers it) ---

This project is AI-friendly by design. "DO WHAT THE FUCK YOU WANT TO"
explicitly includes, with no further permission needed:

  - Training, fine-tuning, or prompting any model on this code.
  - Opening pull requests full of AI-generated code ("slop"). It is
    welcome and reviewed on the same footing as human-written code.
  - Shipping derivatives without disclosing whether a human or a model
    wrote any part of them.

Go wild.
